was%20released%20across%205%2C000%20screens%20in%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%2C%20and%20Hindi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fgoat-kerala-box-office-collections-day-1-vijay-starrer-collects-more-than-rs-4-crores%2Farticleshow%2F113112057.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20Raids%20Ex%20RG%20Kar%20Principal's%20Residence%20In%20Corruption%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Friday%20conducted%20raids%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20found%20brutally%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20college%20last%20month%2C%20sparking%20nationwide%20outrage%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20and%20women%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20has%20conducted%20raids%20at%20locations%20connected%20to%20Ghosh%20and%20his%20three%20associates%20including%20his%20Beliaghata%20residence%20and%20two%20locations%20in%20Howrah%20and%20Subhasgram.%20The%20house%20of%20Prasun%20Chatterjee%2C%20the%20hospital's%20data%20entry%20operator%2C%20was%20also%20searched%20by%20the%20ED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20these%20places%20around%206.15%20am%20and%20started%20our%20raids%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhosh%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20at%20the%20hospital%20during%20his%20tenure.%20The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20granted%20the%20CBI%20three%20weeks%20to%20submit%20a%20progress%20report%20on%20the%20investigation%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20presented%20on%20September%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EED%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20to%20probe%20money%20laundering%20charges%20against%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20in%20the%20financial%20irregularities%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Principal%20has%20undergone%20two%20rounds%20of%20polygraph%20tests%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20rape-murder%20case%20after%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20negligence%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20including%20failing%20to%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20when%20the%20woman's%20body%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20does%20not%20face%20charges%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20doctor%2C%20he%20does%20face%20non-bailable%20corruption%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20suspended%20him%20as%20he%20was%20placed%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20eight%20days.%20The%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20has%20also%20suspended%20his%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20has%20also%20come%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20questioned%20his%20role%20in%20the%20horrific%20crime%2C%20underlining%2C%20that%20the%20delay%20in%20filing%20a%20police%20case%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20FIR%20lodged%20almost%2014%20hours%20after%20discovery%20of%20the%20body...%20the%20Principal%20of%20the%20college%20should%20have%20come%20straightaway%20and%20directed%20filing%20of%20the%20FIR.%20Who%20was%20he%20in%20touch%20with%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20one%20arrest%20has%20been%20made%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20doctor%20-%20a%20police%20volunteer%20called%20Sanjoy%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20each%20other%20over%20alleged%20inaction%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20victim%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20initially%20tried%20to%20suppress%20the%20case%20and%20close%20it%20without%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20tried%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20case.%20We%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20see%20the%20body%20and%20had%20to%20wait%20at%20the%20police%20station%20while%20the%20body%20was%20taken%20for%20post-mortem%20examinations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20father%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725595020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7ca4ss1_-sandeep-ghosh_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-raids-ex-rg-kar-principals-residence-in-corruption-case-6501679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Friday%20conducted%20raids%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-raids-ex-rg-kar-principals-residence-in-corruption-case-6501679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kamala%20wants%20to%20destroy%20...%20'%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20warns%20of%20risks%20if%20Harris%20becomes%20US%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725594498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113111530%2Cimgsize-1006432.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-wants-to-destroy-elon-musk-warns-of-risks-if-harris-becomes-us-president%2Farticleshow%2F113109729.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113109729.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EElon%20