us%20event%2C%20an%20official%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-official-objects-to-loud-dj-music-beaten-with-sticks-cops-6501930%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Gambhir%20Replaced%20Dravid%20As%20Coach%2C%20Pant%20Reveals%20Big%20Change%20In%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20era%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20started%20with%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20Tour.%20While%20India%20won%20the%20T20I%20series%2C%20they%20lost%20the%20ODI%20series.%20Indian%20cricket%C2%A0%20team%20got%20a%20long%20break%20after%20that%20and%20will%20next%20be%20playing%20in%20a%20Test%20series%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20starting%20September%2019.%20That%20series%20will%20start%20Gambhir's%20real%20test.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20going%20to%20be%20crucial%20cog%20in%20India's%20scheme%20of%20things%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Both%20Gambhir%20and%20Pant%20played%20their%20national%20level%20cricket%20for%20Delhi%20team.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20Pant%20talked%20about%20the%20change%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20under%20Gautam%20Gambhir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20biggest%20change%20that%20can%20happen%20under%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20how%20it%20can%20take%20Indian%20cricket%20forward%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20anchor%20asked%20Pant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20Rahul%20bhai%20was%20very%20balanced%20as%20a%20human%20being%20and%20as%20a%20coach.%20It%20could%20be%20both%20good%20and%20bad%2C%20because%20in%20cricket%20there%20can%20be%20positives.%20This%20is%20upon%20the%20individuals%20whether%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20positives%20and%20negatives%2C%20and%20it%20depends%20on%20where%20individuals%20want%20to%20focus.%20Gauti%20bhai%20(Gambhir)%20is%20more%20aggressive%2C%20he's%20very%20one-sided%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20have%20to%20win.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20find%20the%20right%20balance%20and%20improve.%20This%20is%20the%20best%20part%20of%20international%20cricket%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pant%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiocinema.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fin-conversation-with-rishabh-pant%2F4017498%3FmediaID%3D4017498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJio%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%C2%A0Pant%C2%A0warned%20against%20taking%20Bangladesh%20lightly%20in%20the%20upcoming%20two-Test%20series%2C%20and%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20India%20to%20keep%20improving%20themselves%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20competition.%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20recently%20blanked%20Pakistan%202-0%20at%20Rawalpindi%2C%20will%20face%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20side%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20Chennai%20from%20September%2019%20before%20moving%20to%20Kanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20play%20a%20total%20of%2010%20Tests%20within%20the%20next%20five%20months%20as%20the%20series%20against%20Bangladesh%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20three%20Tests%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20in%20October-November%20before%20moving%20to%20Australia%20for%20the%20five-Test%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAsian%20countries%20like%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20perform%20well%20in%20Asian%20conditions%20because%20they%20are%20accustomed%20to%20the%20wickets%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Pant%C2%A0told%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20we%20focus%20solely%20on%20our%20own%20standards%20and%20how%20we%20can%20improve.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20play%20with%20the%20same%20intensity%20and%20give%20our%20100%20percent%20every%20single%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%C2%A0said%20no%20series%20can%20be%20taken%20lightly%20with%20the%20margins%20between%20the%20teams%20decreasing%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPressure%20will%20always%20be%20there%20because%20in%20international%20cricket%2C%20you%20can't%20take%20any%20series%20lightly.%20The%20margin%20between%20winning%20and%20losing%20is%20very%20small%2C%20and%20nowadays%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20international%20teams%20isn't%20much%20either%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%C2%A0said%20playing%20in%20the%20Duleep%20Trophy%20ahead%20of%20a%20long%20season%20of%20Test%20cricket%20will%20give%20the%20players%20quality%20match%20practice%20while%20young%20cricketers%20at%20domestic%20level%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20presence%20of%20international%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725592740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fivd68ito_gautam-gambhir-and-ajit-agarkar-afp_625x300_27_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-very-one-sided-about-rishabh-pants-mega-comment-on-change-in-indian-cricket-6499319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20replaced%20Rahul%20Dravid%20as%20Team%20India's%20head%20coach.%20According%20to%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20one%20big%20change%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20team%20since%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-very-one-sided-about-rishabh-pants-mega-comment-on-change-in-indian-cricket-6499319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20elections%202024%3A%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20nec