v.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-reserves-order-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-request-6498990%5C%22%3Etop%20court%20on%20Thursday%20reserved%20its%20order%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20separate%20pleas%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20bail%20and%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20alleged%20excise%20policy%20scam.%20He%20has%20filed%20two%20separate%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20denial%20of%20bail%20and%20against%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20the%20corruption%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20maintainability%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20pleas%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S%20V%20Raju%20said%20that%20the%20AAP%20chief%20went%20to%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20without%20going%20to%20the%20sessions%20court.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20even%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20which%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20challenged%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20back%20by%20the%20Supreme%20court%20to%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20approached%20the%20High%20court%20without%20going%20to%20the%20sessions%20court.%20This%20is%20my%20preliminary%20objection.%20On%20merits%2C%20trial%20court%20could%20have%20seen%20it%20first.%20The%20high%20court%20was%20made%20to%20see%20merits%20and%20it%20can%20only%20be%20in%20exceptional%20cases.%20In%20ordinary%20cases%2C%20sessions%20court%20has%20to%20be%20approached%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20extraordinary%20person%20who%20requires%20different%20approach.%20When%20all%20other%20Aam%20Aaadmis%20(common%20people)%20go%20to%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20bail%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20special%20treatment%20for%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20told%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Supreme%20Court%20grants%20bail%20to%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C