such%20as%20grand%20jury%20transcripts%2C%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20legal%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20quite%20possible%20that%20there%20will%20be%20some%20new%20information%20that%20will%20come%20out%20well%20before%20there%20will%20be%20actual%20trial%20testimony%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Weisberg%2C%20a%20criminal%20law%20professor%20at%20Stanford%20Law%20School%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20Thursday%20court%20hearing%2C%20Judge%20Tanya%20S.%20Chutkan%20set%20a%20timeline%20for%20several%20filings%20from%20the%20prosecutors%20and%20defense.%20In%20establishing%20deadlines%2C%20the%20judge%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcourt%20is%20not%20concerned%20with%20the%20electoral%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F09%2F05%2Ftrump-jan-6-case-hearing%2F%23link-LQ7JAXJ6MVD7LKGG6WU4N54VZI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20deadline%20requests%20that%20special%20counsel%20Jack%20Smith's%20team%20file%20a%20brief%20by%20September%2026%20on%20the%20former%20president's%20immunity%20in%20light%20of%20a%20recent%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-trump-immunity-january-6-election-ruling-decision-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20gave%20the%20president%20partial%20immunity%20for%20official%20acts%20he%20took%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Reinert%2C%20a%20criminal%20and%20constitutional%20law%20expert%20at%20the%20Cardozo%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20possible%20those%20filings%20could%20include%20some%20new%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20expect%20there%20to%20be%20evidence%20we%20haven't%20seen%20included%20in%20the%20filings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20know%20that%2