0October%207%20Invasion%20Of%20Israel%20Days%20In%20Advance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20forecast%20that%20went%20largely%20unnoticed%2C%20Yigal%20Carmon%2C%20a%20prominent%20counter-terrorism%20expert%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20Media%20Research%20Institute%20(MEMRI)%2C%20predicted%20Hamas'%20violent%20invasion%20of%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20a%20month%20before%20it%20occurred.%20His%20article%2C%20published%20on%20August%2031%2C%202023%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BSigns%20of%20Possible%20War%20in%20September-October%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20open-source%20warnings%20that%20accurately%20pinpointed%20the%20specific%20timeframe%20of%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%2C%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20launched%20a%20devastating%20invasion%20into%20southern%20Israel%2C%20resulting%20in%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20attacks%20in%20the%20country's%20recent%20history.%20The%20violence%20left%20nearly%201%2C200%20dead%2C%20and%20over%20250%20individuals%20abducted.%20The%20massacre%20rattled%20Israel%20and%20shocked%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20counter-offensive%2C%20Israel%20launched%20wave%20after%20wave%20of%20attacks%20into%20Gaza%2C%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20territory%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLately%20there%20have%20been%20growing%20indications%20that%20a%20war%20against%20Israel%20may%20break%20out%20in%20September%20or%20October%202023.%20The%20trigger%20may%20be%20spiraling%20violent%20clashes%20resulting%20in%20many%20casualties%2C%20or%20the%20use%20of%20new%20weapons%20leading%20to%20many%20fatalities%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20which%20Israel%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20suffice%20with%20its%20regular%20counterterrorism%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.memri.org%2Freports%2Fsigns-possible-war-september-october%5C%22%3ECarmon%20wrote%20in%20August%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20neither%20Hamas%20nor%20Hizbullah%20are%20eager%20to%20start%20a%20comprehensive%20confrontation%20with%20Israel%2C%20such%20a%20confrontation%20could%20result%20from%20an%20uncontrolled%20deterioration%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20from%20the%20use%20of%20new%20and%20unusually%20deadly%20weapons%20by%20these%20movements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20August%20prediction%20stemmed%20from%20rising%20tensions%20on%20Israel's%20borders%2C%20coupled%20with%20Hezbollah's%20increasing%20territorial%20demands%20and%20challenges%20to%20Israel's%20sovereignty.%20In%20his%20analysis%2C%20Carmon%20warned%20that%20while%20neither%20Hamas%20nor%20Hezbollah%20seemed%20eager%20for%20an%20all-out%20war%2C%20the%20volatile%20conditions%20on%20the%20ground%20could%20easily%20spiral%20into%20a%20larger%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Jewish%20holidays%20in%20September%20and%20October%2C%20Jews%20are%20likely%20to%20visit%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20compound%2C%20as%20happens%20every%20year.%20Hamas%20and%20Hizbullah%20spokesmen%20have%20stressed%20that%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20regional%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20devastating%20regional%20conflict%20continues%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20have%20been%20largely%20unsuccessful.%20A%20series%20of%20meetings%20in%20Qatar%20between%20stakeholders%20on%20both%20sides%20have%20yielded%20no%20tangible%20solution%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725586620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjvvgvfd_israelhamas-war-reuters_625x300_04_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-man-who-predicted-hamas-october-7-invasion-of-israel-days-in-advance-6501567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20forecast%20that%20went%20largely%20unnoticed