main%20has%20since%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20festival%20website%20and%20McFarland%20himself%2C%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20tickets%20has%20already%20sold%20out%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20difficult%20to%20verify%20that%20claim.%20At%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20people%20seem%20to%20have%20genuinely%20bought%20tickets%2C%20though%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftravel%2F2023%2F08%2F22%2Ffyre-festival-2-billy-mcfarland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Ffyre-festival-2-tickets-sold-out-billy-mcfarland-couple%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20both%20spoke%20to%20Victoria%20Medvedenko%2C%20who%20purchased%20tickets%20for%20her%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20at%20%24549.89%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedvedenko%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20nursing%20student%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftravel%2F2023%2F08%2F22%2Ffyre-festival-2-billy-mcfarland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20wasn't%20very%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20festival%20might%20turn%20out.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sure%20I'll%20get%20my%20money%20back%20so%20I%20don't%20really%20see%20it%20as%20much%20of%20a%20loss%20either%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20boyfriend%2C%20Cooper%20Sinkiawic%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Ffyre-festival-2-tickets-sold-out-billy-mcfarland-couple%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20couple's%20biggest%20worry%20was%20whether%20major%20acts%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20sign%20on%20to%20the%20festival.%20While%20they're%20%26quot%3Boptimistic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20they're%20not%20ruling%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20%26quot%3Bsome%20cheese%20sandwiches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheese%20sandwich%20Fyre%20Festival%20documentary%20Netflix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dbf396fe94e8613b0549c23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iconic%20cheese%20sandwich%20photo%20from%20Fyre%20Festival%20that%20went%20viral.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcFarland%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCwP5Qz8gP5n%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igshid%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20since-deleted%20statement%20on%20his%20Instagram%20in%20August%202023%20that%20all%20revenue%20from%20ticket%20sales%20would%20be%20held%20in%20escrow%20until%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20final%20date%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0meaning%20that%20a%20third%20party%20will%20hold%20them%20until%20that%20condition%20is%20satisfied.%20In%20his%20WSJ%20interview%2C%20McFarland%20reiterated%20that%20the%20money%20from%20the%20aforementioned%20sales%20remains%20in%20escrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209966ed6-2ed5-4a34-8c2c-7208e1912270%5C%22%3EWho's%20on%20the%20lineup%20for%20Fyre%20Festival%20II%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20one%20yet.%20So%2C%20again%3A%20TBD!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcFarland%20told%20the%20WSJ%20that%20he%20has%20a%20few%20ideas%20for%20potential%20entertainers%2C%20including%20Karate%20Combat%2C%20a%20karate%20fighting%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20other%20events%2C%20McFarland%20said%20in%20his%20announcement%20video%20that%20he%20was%20working%20with%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20best%20TV%20companies%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20to%20produce%20yet%20another%20documentary%20titled%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Fyre.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20he%20was%20working%20with%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20biggest%20production%20companies%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20deal%20to%20produce%20%26quot%3BFyre%20Festival%3A%20The%20Broadway%20Musical%2C%26quot%3B%2