g%20steam.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20briefly%20continued%20its%20retreat%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20following%20a%20report%20that%20the%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-price-market-cap-decline-subpoena-antitrust-probe-ai-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20a%20subpoena%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20In%20all%2C%20the%20stock%20has%20fallen%20by%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20since%20Nvidia%20released%20its%20second-quarter%20earnings%20in%20late%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20the%20post-earnings%20skid%20marks%20a%20buying%20opportunity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20released%20Thursday%2C%20the%20bank%20said%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20now%20hovering%20around%20its%20cheapest%20valuation%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20market%20forces%20could%20enhance%20near-term%20stock%20volatility%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20find%20NVDA%20valuation%20compelling%20at%2027x%20CY25%2FFY26E%20consensus%20PE%20(or%20only%20~20x%20PE%20at%20high-end%20of%20%245%2B%20CY25%20eps%20estimate)%2C%26quot%3B%20analyst%20Vivek%20Arya%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20this%2C%20Nvidia%20price-to-earnings%20have%20ranged%20between%20the%20mid-20s%20to%20mid-60s%20over%20the%20past%20half-decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20who%20buy%20the%20stock%20now%20could%20be%20facing%2054%25%20upside%2C%20according%20to%20BofA's%20price%20target%20of%20%24165%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20looks%20achievable%2C%20as%20Nvidia%20will%20remain%20a%20key%20beneficiary%20of%20AI%20investing%20and%20won't%20always%20be%20pressured%20down%20by%20headwinds%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%20For%20instance%2C%20weak%20supply-side%20fundamentals%20should%20subside%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20the%20analysts%20noted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20investors%20are%20disappointed%20by%20delays%20in%20the%20firm's%20next-gen%20Blackwell%20chip%2C%20shipments%20should%20be%20confirmed%20over%20the%20next%20several%20weeks%2C%20BofA%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20the%20bank%20doesn't%20anticipate%20demand%20for%20prior-gen%20Hopper%20chips%20to%20disappear%2C%20given%20how%20strong%20AI%20demand%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerning%20regulatory%20headwinds%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-subpoena-nvidia-antitrust-investigation-heats-up-report-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenied%20receiving%20a%20subpoena%20from%20the%20DOJ.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20%E2%80%94%20which%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20subpoena%20%E2%80%94%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-04%2Fnvidia-says-it-has-not-been-subpoenaed-by-justice-department%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-americas%26sref%3DyaJhKSOh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20DOJ%20sent%20a%20civil%20investigative%20demand%2C%20citing%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20BofA%20assumes%20no%20impact%20from%20these%20developments%2C%20it%20noted%20that%20government%20cases%20are%20not%20uncommon%20against%20large%20US%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20skepticism%20about%20AI's%20potential%20remains%20a%20non-issue%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20at%20least%20until%202026.%20Those%20concerned%20that%20the%20AI%20spending%20wave%20has%20yet%20to%20show%20results%20must%20simply%20be%20patient%2C%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tech%20industry%20will%20give%20itself%20at%20least%20another%201-2%20years%20of%20intense%20buildout%20of%20NVDA%20Blackwell%20chip%20with%20its%204x%20lift%20in%20AI%20training%20and%2025x%2B%20lift%20in%20inference.%20Efforts%20thus%20far%20with%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20large%20language%20models%20(LLM)%2C%20using%20NVDA%20Hopper%20was%20just%20the%20teaser%2C%26quot%3B%20BofA%20wrote%2C%20anticipating%20